<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
    
    <head>
        <title>SuperSnake</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/mainPageStyles.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/snakeStyles.css"/>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/loginStyles.css"/>
        <script src="js/snake.js"></script>
        <script src="js/mainPage.js"></script>
    </head>

    <div id="loginBox">
        <form id="loginForm" method="POST" action="http://localhost:5000/pathLogged">
            <button class="closeForm" onclick="openLogin()">X</button>
            <div id="registerButton">
                <p>NEW ACCOUNT </p>
                <label class="switch">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="isRegister" onclick="showRegister()">
                    <span class="slider"></span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <p>USERNAME</p>
            <input id="loginUserName" type="text" name="userName">
            <p>PASSWORD</p>
            <input id="loginPass" type="password" name="pass1">
            <p id="hydeOnLogin1">REPEAT PASSWORD</p>
            <input id="hydeOnLogin2" type="password" name="pass2">
            <button id="loginButton">LOGIN</button>
        </form>
    </div>

    <body>
        <div id="nav-bar">
            <button id="navMenu" onclick="openNav()">
                <img id="navMenuIcon" src="images/menuIcon.jpg" alt="menu icon">
            </button>
            <div id="frontText">
                <h1 id="title">SuperSnake</h1>
                <h1 id="userName" onclick="openLogin()"><%=dataToUse.userName%></h1>
                <button id="logoutButton" onclick="goGuest()">Logout</button>
            </div>
            <img id="userIcon" src="<%=dataToUse.image%>" class="fitIcon" alt="user icon" onclick="openLogin()">
        </div>

        <div id="navMenuContent" class = "sidenav">
            <a href="#jumpToGame">Game</a>
            <a href="#jumpToLeaderboard">Leaderboard</a>
            <a href="#jumpInfo">Rules</a>
        </div>

        <div id="main-content">
            <form id="backToGuest" method="POST" action="http://localhost:5000/pathGuest"></form>
            <form id="updateScor" method="POST" action="http://localhost:5000/pathLoggedUpdate">
                <input type="text" style="visibility: collapse; height: 0;" id="updateScorInServer" name="score">
            </form>
            <jumper id="jumpToGame" style="margin-bottom: 0px"></jumper>
            <div id="snakeBoard">
                <button id="playButton" onclick="StartGame()">
                    <div class="arrow-right"></div>
                </button>
            </div>
            <h6 id="textScore">Score: 0</h6>
            <jumper id="jumpToLeaderboard" style="margin-bottom: 0px"></jumper>
            <div id="leaderboardGrid">
                <div id="leaderboardTable">
                    <h1>Leaderboard</h1>
                    <div>
                        <name><%=dataToUse.high[0].userName%></name>
                        <score><%=dataToUse.high[0].score%></score>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <name><%=dataToUse.high[1].userName%></name>
                        <score><%=dataToUse.high[1].score%></score>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <name><%=dataToUse.high[2].userName%></name>
                        <score><%=dataToUse.high[2].score%></score>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <name><%=dataToUse.high[3].userName%></name>
                        <score><%=dataToUse.high[3].score%></score>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <name><%=dataToUse.high[4].userName%></name>
                        <score><%=dataToUse.high[4].score%></score>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div id="myRecord">
                    <h2>My record</h2>
                    <p><%=dataToUse.score%></p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <jumper id="jumpInfo" style="margin-bottom: 60px;"></jumper>
            <h1 id="rulesTitle">Rules</h1>
            <div class="line"></div>
            <div id="info">
                <p> &emsp; The idea behind SuperSnake is to get as many points
                    as possible, the length of the snake in one level or
                    the number of levels are irrelevant here.
                </p>
                <div id="firstRule">Score: 999</div>
                <p> &emsp; Collect stars to grow your snake. At each level, when
                    you reach the length of 17, a special star will appear that can
                    teleport you to the next level. But before you go to the next
                    level, it's worth noting that super stars will appear on each level
                    when your snake grows very large. Those stars give you double the
                    points of regular stars. Even more, regular stars are more valuable
                    in higher levels.
                </p>
                <div id="secondRule">
                    <img src="images/goldenStar.png" class="fitIcon" alt="golden star">
                    <img src="images/levelStar.png" alt="golden star">
                </div>
                <p>
                    &emsp; Be careful! Every 5 levels the snake speed will increase and
                    it will be harder and harder to get the stars. And also make sure 
                    your snake doesn't touch any of the walls you encounter.
                </p>
                <div id="thirdRule">
                    <div class="triangle" style="grid-column: 1;"></div>
                    <div class="triangle" style="grid-column: 2;"></div>
                    <div class="triangle" style="grid-column: 3;"></div>
                </div>
                <p>
                    &emsp; Before you go, be careful at the walls at each start of the level.
                    They can really take you by surprise sometimes. Have fun!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>